data.description: Discover modern convenience in this charming 1933 built ranch featuring 2 beds, 1 bath, and a dry, full size basement with generous storage space! The roof was replaced in 2016 and insulation fully redone in 2011 (per the original seller disclosures). Hardwood flooring enhances both bedrooms and the living room, while a modernized kitchen and bath add a touch of contemporary elegance. You won't want to miss out on this vintage gem, blending history with modern comforts. Schedule your own private tour today!
